  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2825600/extras/08b072243c85e33dbe56e22a2bf26848.avif?t=1758293699\" width=616 height=100 /></span>​</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Step into a miniature world where toy trains chug through nostalgic environments like living rooms, couch forts, attics, and picnic blankets- all lovingly crafted as cozy dioramas filled with nostalgic charm. Teeny Tiny Trains is a laid-back puzzle game that captures the wonder of childhood playrooms and the satisfying click of a well-placed track.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2825600/extras/9ef30e760077cfa7ff82aae210444251.poster.avif?t=1758293699\" width=608 height=350 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2825600/extras/9ef30e760077cfa7ff82aae210444251.webm?t=1758293699\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2825600/extras/9ef30e760077cfa7ff82aae210444251.mp4?t=1758293699\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As the clever conductor of your own teeny railway, you’ll solve bite-sized puzzles by laying down tracks, navigating whimsical obstacles, and guiding your trains to their destinations. Each level is a handcrafted brain teaser designed to spark joy, reward experimentation, and make you smile.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2825600/extras/d67c398dae36d7344acb240f3d724a76.avif?t=1758293699\" width=616 height=100 /></span></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Charming Track-Building Puzzles</strong> – Use switches, splitters, bridges, and more to guide your trains through clever routing challenges.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2825600/extras/20cc2ae880371b8f4e42c26e31affe74.poster.avif?t=1758293699\" width=608 height=350 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2825600/extras/20cc2ae880371b8f4e42c26e31affe74.webm?t=1758293699\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2825600/extras/20cc2ae880371b8f4e42c26e31affe74.mp4?t=1758293699\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Strategic Yet Relaxing</strong> – Thoughtful puzzles that challenge your brain without pressure. Just good vibes.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Create and Share with the Level Editor</strong> – Build your own cozy conundrums and explore puzzles from the community.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2825600/extras/c4a80fc28be3152a405f98f19e74b7ad.poster.avif?t=1758293699\" width=608 height=350 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2825600/extras/c4a80fc28be3152a405f98f19e74b7ad.webm?t=1758293699\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2825600/extras/c4a80fc28be3152a405f98f19e74b7ad.mp4?t=1758293699\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Collect and Customize</strong> – Unlock a variety of adorable engines and cars inspired by classic toys as you flip through the toy catalogue.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Nostalgic, Diorama-Style Environments</strong> – Each level is a love letter to childhood spaces, filled with cozy detail.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Play the Traincade!</strong> – Visit the in-game retro arcade cabinet packed with train-themed twists on classic games. Yes, <i>Train Invaders</i> is a thing, you’re welcome. </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2825600/extras/308d672d89161217fb1ac387ddf31dc9.poster.avif?t=1758293699\" width=608 height=350 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2825600/extras/308d672d89161217fb1ac387ddf31dc9.webm?t=1758293699\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2825600/extras/308d672d89161217fb1ac387ddf31dc9.mp4?t=1758293699\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >It’s a game built on memories, the click of a wooden track on a carpet, the excitement of circling your dream engine in a toy catalog, the glow of an old arcade screen with your favorite game ready to go.  It’s a cozy, handcrafted world that invites you to slow down, think creatively, and find joy in making things work, one tiny train at a time.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2825600/extras/08b072243c85e33dbe56e22a2bf26848.avif?t=1758293699\" width=616 height=100 /></span>​</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Step into a miniature world where toy trains chug through nostalgic environments like living rooms, couch forts, attics, and picnic blankets- all lovingly crafted as cozy dioramas filled with nostalgic charm. Teeny Tiny Trains is a laid-back puzzle game that captures the wonder of childhood playrooms and the satisfying click of a well-placed track.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2825600/extras/9ef30e760077cfa7ff82aae210444251.poster.avif?t=1758293699\" width=608 height=350 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2825600/extras/9ef30e760077cfa7ff82aae210444251.webm?t=1758293699\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2825600/extras/9ef30e760077cfa7ff82aae210444251.mp4?t=1758293699\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As the clever conductor of your own teeny railway, you’ll solve bite-sized puzzles by laying down tracks, navigating whimsical obstacles, and guiding your trains to their destinations. Each level is a handcrafted brain teaser designed to spark joy, reward experimentation, and make you smile.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2825600/extras/d67c398dae36d7344acb240f3d724a76.avif?t=1758293699\" width=616 height=100 /></span></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Charming Track-Building Puzzles</strong> – Use switches, splitters, bridges, and more to guide your trains through clever routing challenges.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2825600/extras/20cc2ae880371b8f4e42c26e31affe74.poster.avif?t=1758293699\" width=608 height=350 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2825600/extras/20cc2ae880371b8f4e42c26e31affe74.webm?t=1758293699\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2825600/extras/20cc2ae880371b8f4e42c26e31affe74.mp4?t=1758293699\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Strategic Yet Relaxing</strong> – Thoughtful puzzles that challenge your brain without pressure. Just good vibes.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Create and Share with the Level Editor</strong> – Build your own cozy conundrums and explore puzzles from the community.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2825600/extras/c4a80fc28be3152a405f98f19e74b7ad.poster.avif?t=1758293699\" width=608 height=350 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2825600/extras/c4a80fc28be3152a405f98f19e74b7ad.webm?t=1758293699\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2825600/extras/c4a80fc28be3152a405f98f19e74b7ad.mp4?t=1758293699\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Collect and Customize</strong> – Unlock a variety of adorable engines and cars inspired by classic toys as you flip through the toy catalogue.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Nostalgic, Diorama-Style Environments</strong> – Each level is a love letter to childhood spaces, filled with cozy detail.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Play the Traincade!</strong> – Visit the in-game retro arcade cabinet packed with train-themed twists on classic games. Yes, <i>Train Invaders</i> is a thing, you’re welcome. </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2825600/extras/308d672d89161217fb1ac387ddf31dc9.poster.avif?t=1758293699\" width=608 height=350 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2825600/extras/308d672d89161217fb1ac387ddf31dc9.webm?t=1758293699\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2825600/extras/308d672d89161217fb1ac387ddf31dc9.mp4?t=1758293699\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >It’s a game built on memories, the click of a wooden track on a carpet, the excitement of circling your dream engine in a toy catalog, the glow of an old arcade screen with your favorite game ready to go.  It’s a cozy, handcrafted world that invites you to slow down, think creatively, and find joy in making things work, one tiny train at a time.</p>",
